'''''Empire'' 27''' is the twenty-seventh issue in the ''[[Star Wars: Empire]]'' series of comics. It was published on [[December 15]], [[2004]] by [[Dark Horse Comics]].

==Publisher's summary==
''Luke Skywalker is a pilot for the Rebel Alliance and a Jedi-in-training, but when a Rebel intel team gets pinned down by an unexpected Imperial patrol, Luke receives an unexpected promotion &ndash; to General! It's all part of Commander Narra's plan to enlist the aid of an unexpected ally that could turn the tables on the Imperials.''

==Opening crawl==
{{OpeningCrawl
|name="GENERAL" SKYWALKER (part 2)
|text=During a covert operation to set up an unmanned listening post on an uncharted
planet, Luke Skywalker, commander Narra, and the Rebel Intel team are caught
on the ground by an Imperial patrol. While trying to escape the Imperials,
Luke and Narra encounter a third party - someone who has been on the planet
for a long time...}}

